com.twiddles.ganesha.functionality
Class JenaFile

java.lang.Object
  com.twiddles.ganesha.functionality.JenaFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
RDFFile
public class JenaFile
extends java.lang.Object
implements RDFFile

Implementation of RDFFile using Jena.

This requires the Jena API to be installed on your system and listed in java's CLASSPATH.

getFileName

public java.lang.String getFileName()
Returns the name of the file from which the currently loaded RDF data originates. This is usually the name of the file which was loaded unless a new file has been created since then or the data was written to a different file.

shorten

public static java.lang.String shorten(java.lang.String uri)
Shortens the URIs of properties. First it checks with a set of predefined descriptions of common properties. If no match is found the last part of the property's URI is chopped off and returned.

Parameters:
uri - the property uri to shorten
Returns:
a short description
